snippet.title: Biomes of Icarus - 4K Preview
snippet.description:
On Icarus a range of Earth-like and exotic biomes - each with their own storms, ecosystems and hand-crafted terrains - will challenge your survival skills like no game has before.

Pre order Icarus now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1149460/ICARUS/

Join our Discord:
https://discord.com/invite/surviveicarus

Follow us on Twitch:
https://www.twitch.tv/surviveicarus
